paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted information on genetic variants in the KCNH2 gene, including penetrance data.

functional_data.summary: Significant association with clinical outcomes (SCA plus syncope).

variants.additional_notes: The variant showed protective effects in all BrS patients regardless of SCN5A variants.
key_quotes: Only the SNP, rs2968863, showed protective effects in all BrS patients no matter whether they had an SCN5A variant or not.

extraction_metadata.notes: Only one variant in KCNH2 was reported in the paper.
